    "answer": "AC",
    "explanation": "【핵심 용어】\n▸ AWS Direct Connect — 전용 네트워크 연결\n▸ Private VIF — 비공개 인터페이스\n▸ S3 Interface Endpoint — VPC 내 S3 접근\n【정답 포인트】\n▸ A: Direct Connect (Private VIF) → 온프레미스 연결\n▸ C: Interface Endpoint → 다중 계정 S3 접근\n【오답 체크】\n(B) Public VIF는 인터넷 거쳐감 (비공개 아님)\n(D) Gateway Endpoint는 직접 연결 계정에만 유효\n(E) VPC Peering은 한계: 3개 계정 확장 불가\n【시험 포인트】\nMulti-account + Private + No internet → Direct Connect + Interface EP",
    "en_q": "A company wants to send data from its on-premises systems to Amazon S3 buckets. The company created the S3 buckets in three different accounts. The company must send the data privately without the data traveling across the internet. The company has no existing dedicated connectivity to AWS. Which combination of steps should a solutions architect take to meet these requirements? (Choose two.)",
