    "answer": "B",
    "explanation": "【핵심 용어】\n▸ AWS Batch — 배치 작업용 서비스\n▸ Spot Instances — 비용 최소화\n【정답 포인트】\n▸ (B) Batch: 배치 작업(15-20GB) 최적화\n▸ Spot 전용: \"중단 견딜 수 있음\" → 가장 저렴\n▸ SPOT_CAPACITY_OPTIMIZED: 중단 최소화\n【오답 체크】\n(A) Lambda: 15GB 처리 시 Lambda 한계(메모리 10GB), 비용 높음\n(C) On-Demand + Spot: Spot만으로 충분, On-Demand 비용 낭비\n(D) EKS: Batch보다 복잡, 오버헤드 높음\n【시험 포인트】\n\"배치 + 중단 허용 + 비용 최소\"는 AWS Batch + Spot Instance의 필수 조합입니다.",
    "en_q": "A company needs to run large batch-processing jobs on data that is stored in an Amazon S3 bucket. The jobs perform simulations. The results of the jobs are not time sensitive, and the process can withstand interruptions. Each job must process 15-20 GB of data when the data is stored in the S3 bucket. The company will store the output from the jobs in a different Amazon S3 bucket for further analysis. Which solution will meet these requirements MOST cost-effectively?",
